+## Directory Structure
+
+| Directory | Purpose |
+|-----------|---------|
+| `services/home-miner-daemon/` | Daemon implementation (daemon.py, cli.py, store.py, spine.py) |
+| `apps/zend-home-gateway/` | Mobile command center UI (single HTML file) |
+| `scripts/` | Operational scripts (bootstrap, pair, control) |
