+
+## Data Flow
+
+### Control Command Flow
+
+```
+User/Agent
+    в”Ӯ
+    в”Ӯ cli.py control --action set_mode --mode balanced
+    в”Ӯ
+    в–ј
+cli.py
+    в”Ӯ
+    в”Ӯ 1. Check capability via store.py
+    в”Ӯ 2. POST /miner/set_mode to daemon.py
+    в”Ӯ 3. On success, append event via spine.py
+    в”Ӯ
+    в–ј
+daemon.py (GatewayHandler)
+    в”Ӯ
+    в”Ӯ 1. Validate request (JSON, mode field)
+    в”Ӯ 2. Call miner.set_mode("balanced")
+    в”Ӯ
+    в–ј
+MinerSimulator
+    в”Ӯ
+    в”Ӯ 1. Acquire lock
+    в”Ӯ 2. Update mode
+    в”Ӯ 3. Update hashrate based on mode
+    в”Ӯ 4. Return success
+    в”Ӯ
+    в–ј
+CLI prints receipt
+spine.py appends control_receipt
+```
+
+### Status Query Flow
+
+```
+User (browser or CLI)
+    в”Ӯ
+    в”Ӯ GET /status or fetch /status
+    в”Ӯ
+    в–ј
+daemon.py (GatewayHandler)
+    в”Ӯ
+    в”Ӯ 1. Call miner.get_snapshot()
+    в”Ӯ
+    в–ј
+MinerSimulator.get_snapshot()
+    в”Ӯ
+    в”Ӯ 1. Acquire lock
+    в”Ӯ 2. Calculate uptime
+    в”Ӯ 3. Return status dict with freshness timestamp
+    в”Ӯ
+    в–ј
+JSON response
+    в”Ӯ
+    в”Ӯ Browser: update UI
+    в”Ӯ CLI: print JSON
+    в”Ӯ
+    в–ј
+User sees current miner state
+```
+
